text: I went to find the Lok Lok place, but I couldn’t find the stall even when I was at 02-05… i then walked the whole of lvl 2 at wcega plaza, but still can’t find the place… I went to the tower but still can’t find the place… I was so disappointed
Seems like a good place to try the food and have some drinks. Please note this shop is only open mon-sat. This stall is located in a Coffeeshop.
